/// TL;DR
3 collectives, 2 Floors, 1 Event. 
F1: Trance and Hard Trance. 
F2: Hard Groove and Hard Techno.

/// DESCRIPTION
TRINITY at M01 Club, Berlin, is a convergence of electronic exploration and communal harmony. Hosted by Cycling Club Collective, MWN KLLKTV, and Obstinsel Kollektiv, this event is a testament to the diverse and powerful spectrum of techno.

The first floor is dedicated to the raw, unfiltered energy of TRANCE and HARD TRANCE, while the second floor elevates the experience with a blend of HARD GROOVE and HARD TECHNO. Special guest DJs, celebrated for their unique styles and electrifying performances, will also grace our decks, adding to the night's dynamic soundscape.

