/// GENERAL RULES
At TRINITY, we are committed to creating a safer and more inclusive space. We uphold a zero-tolerance policy towards any form of discrimination or harassment. This means no sexism, racism, classism, homophobia, xenophobia, or transphobia. We encourage kindness and respect. If you witness or experience anything contrary to these values, please inform our AWARENESS TEAM or any staff member. Inappropriate behavior will lead to an invitation to leave, and entry is at the club's discretion. Remember, no photos or videos, and no GBL/GHB!

Most importantly, SHARE THE LOVE!

